  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>The Hobby Tribe</h1>
        <p>
          In seconds, and beyond human creativity is centred on executing
          repetitive manual processes from Client Work to Client-centered
          solutions to cutting-edge processes in real-time with powerful APIs
          and work without code.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <section class="story-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Letâ€™s Start at the Beginning</h2>
        <div class="story-grid">
          <div class="story-text fade-in">
            <p>
              Initially, Kevin was a freelance web developer working with
              clients. After a decade of writing security extensions,
              experiencing of the client pain points, the fee much work, was
              enough light to find better solutions.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              They knew there needed to be a team-focused solution, so in 2018
              they started building Thres.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="story-card" onmouseenter="animateHeading(this)">
    <h3 class="story-heading">Our Vision</h3>
    <div class="story-content">
      To ignite a world where every individual, especially adults, rediscovers the joy of hobbies and has the opportunity to turn their passion into purpose and profession.
  </div>

  <div class="story-card" onmouseenter="animateHeading(this)">
    <h3 class="story-heading">Our Mission</h3>
    <div class="story-content">
      To build a vibrant community that empowers individuals to explore, develop, and monetize their hobbies through accessible experiences, mentorship, and collaboration.
    </div>
  </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Leadership Section -->
    <section class="leadership-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Our Leadership</h2>
        <div class="leadership-grid">
          <div class="leader-card fade-in">
            <div class="leader-image">
              <img src="/images/Joshua.jpg" />
            </div>
            <div class="leader-info">
              <div class="leader-name">Joshua Salins</div>
              <div class="leader-role">Co-Founder & CEO</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="leader-card fade-in">
            <div class="leader-image">
              <img src="/images/Gaurav.jpg" />
            </div>
            <div class="leader-info">
              <div class="leader-name">Gaurav Mirchandani</div>
              <div class="leader-role">Co-Founder & COO</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="leader-card fade-in">
             <div class="leader-image">
              <img src="/images/Charles1.jpg" />
            </div>
            <div class="leader-info">
              <div class="leader-name">Charles William</div>
              <div class="leader-role">Co-Founder & CTO</div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Backed By Section -->
    <section class="backed-section fade-in">
      <!-- <div class="container"> -->
        <h3 style="font-size: 2rem;">Driven By World-Class Support</h3>
        <div class="logo-globe-wrapper">
        <div class="logo-globe-track">
          <div class="logo-globe-slide">
            <img class="worldclass1" src="/images/worldclass1.png" alt="img1" />
            <img class="worldclass2" src="/images/worldclass2.png" alt="img2" />
            <img class="worldclass3" src="/images/worldclass3.png" alt="img3" />
        </div>
        </div>

    </section>

     <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="values-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Our values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card fade-in">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Simplicity</h3>
            <p>
              We strive for our product, processes, and customer experience to
              be as simple as possible. We consistently simplify by removing
              unnecessary complexity and focusing on the most important and
              impactful work.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card fade-in">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Speed</h3>
            <p>
              We can work to ship be respond and be fast. Speed is what makes us
              competitive versus traditional approaches. We ship fast
              consistently, execute with purpose, and are agile with our
              customers' needs.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card fade-in">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Soundness</h3>
            <p>
              We're determined to achieve our mission and goals, but we want to
              do them with the right people and build a great company. Doing the
              right thing for customers and teammates is what matters most.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Join Team Section -->
    <section class="join-section">
      <div class="join-content fade-in">
        <h2>Join a world-class team</h2>
        <p>
          We have every role important in our automation to creating automation
          and making it accessible to everyone.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/classes"
          class="cta-btn"
          >Do What Your Heart Says</a
        >
      </div>
      <div class="team-photos fade-in">
        <img src="/images/workspace1.jpg" class="team-photo"></img>
        <img src="/images/workspace2.jpg" class="team-photo"></img>
        <img src="/images/workspace3.jpg" class="team-photo"></img>
      </div>
    </section>

